{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Sequencing was carried out using a PromethION with R9.4 flowcells and base-called using Guppy 5.0.11 in the high accuracy (HAC) mode.",
    "Reads were aligned using Minimap2 (v2.26-r1175).",
    "Methylation calling was carried out using Megalodon v2.4.2.",
    "CNV calling was done using QDNAseq v1.18.0 40 and SV calling was carried out using Sniffles2 v2.06 41.",
    "We defined the amplified regions for assembly using the Amplicon architect predictions based on short-read data from the same biopsies."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "CNV calling was done using QDNAseq v1.18.0 40 and SV calling was carried out using Sniffles2 v2.06 41."
  ]
